<SYNC Start=2921920><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2924220><P Class=ENUSCC>私は
<SYNC Start=2926590><P Class=ENUSCC>トカゲの尻尾でしょうか？
<SYNC Start=2929190><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
